title: Connecticut 2008 Presidential Election Results
name: Connecticut 2008 Presidential Election Results
description:
2008 Presidential Election results by town for the state of Connecticut.  Data include the election tally for each town by candidate listed on the Connecticut ballot.  

Data and map compiled by Benjamin Spaulding, Map and Geographic Information Center, Homer Babbidge Library at the University of Connecticut.  For more information visit magic.lib.uconn.edu
